sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Client as Demo.Bff / Demo.RefreshToken / Demo.DeviceCode
    participant Token as TokenController
    participant ClientSvc as ClientService
    participant TokenSvc as TokenService
    participant RTRepo as RefreshTokenRepository

    Client->>Token: POST /connect/token<br/>grant_type=refresh_token
    Token->>ClientSvc: AuthenticateClientAsync
    ClientSvc-->>Token: 客户端认证通过
    Token->>TokenSvc: RefreshAsync(refresh_token, client_id)
    TokenSvc->>RTRepo: FindByTokenAsync
    RTRepo-->>TokenSvc: RefreshToken
    TokenSvc->>TokenSvc: 校验未吊销 / 未过期 / 属于当前 client
    TokenSvc->>RTRepo: RevokeAsync(old refresh_token)
    TokenSvc->>RTRepo: AddAsync(new refresh_token)
    TokenSvc->>TokenSvc: IssueAccessTokenAsync
    TokenSvc-->>Token: 新 access_token + 新 refresh_token
    Token-->>Client: token 响应
